explanation:
According to the German ordinance on the notification procedure for limiting electromagnetic fields (BEMFV), you need to re-report a stationary amateur broadcasting station that is located at a fixed position when:

* You change the location of the antenna or the transmission equipment;
* You increase the effective radiated power by more than 10%;
* You change the frequency band or the transmission mode used;
* The transmission equipment is replaced or significantly modified.

You should submit this report to the competent authority at the Federal Network Agency (BNetzA).
